# Monorepo Conventions

- This repo is a workspace-managed monorepo.
- Apps live in `apps/`, shared libraries in `packages/`, infrastructure in `infra/`, and templates in `templates/`.
- Prefer reusing shared packages over duplicating logic across apps.
- Run repo tasks through root scripts.
- Read `AGENTS.md` and `.memory/project-map.md` before broad exploration.
